def sovereign
  puts "Are you under the rule of a president or a monarch?"
  puts "Enter P or M"
  response = gets.chomp.upcase

  if response == "P"
    puts "
    ║✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
    ║✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
    ║✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
    ║✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭✭▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
    ║▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
    ║▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
    ║▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅▅
